description:
Parole a Catinelle is a fast and fun game for the whole family or a group of friends. Will you or one of your opponents be the first to say the secret word? If you succeed, you earn your first point.

Reach 3 points and you&rsquo;ll be the winner of the match.

Wait for your opponent to say, &ldquo;Let&rsquo;s play another game.&rdquo;

Ham with ham, melon with melon, cheese with cheese.
Combine matching items to create something stronger!

And at the end of it all, what you&rsquo;re aiming for is everyone&rsquo;s favorite&hellip;
&ldquo;Prosciutto melon!&rdquo;

Ah&hellip; but prosciutto with cheese sounds delicious too&hellip;
Hey, can I have that cheese?

This is a card game where you combine identical ingredients to be the first to create prosciutto melon.

The objective of the game is either to reach a set number of points or to obtain a prosciutto melon/prosciutto cheese card.

Animal Code is a game where you must discover a secret combination of cards (the Animal Code). To do this, you'll have to collect and form certain combinations of animals during your turn, which will allow you to gradually reveal the Code. Once you discover it, you must repeat it on your hand and show it to win.

&bull;&bull;&bull;

C&oacute;digo Animal es juego donde deber&aacute;s descubrir una combinaci&oacute;n secreta de cartas (El c&oacute;digo animal). Para esto tendr&aacute;s que juntar y formar ciertas combinaciones de animales durante tu turno que te permitir&aacute;n ir descubriendo el C&oacute;digo de a poco. Una vez que lo descubras deber&aacute;s repetirlo en tu mano y mostrarlo para ganar.
